This command includes Google Test headers, links against pthread (which Google Test requires), includes your test file, the C file containing your `area` function, the main function from Google Test, and links against the Google Test library. Make sure to adjust the paths and file names as needed for your setup.

### Step 5: Execute Your Test Binary

